entry.string: Insert all INTO Error_Repository_tbl (SEQID, INTERFACENAME, SENDER, TARGET, VERBCODE, ERRORCODE, ERRORMSG, SEVERITY, TRANSACTIONID, MESSAGEID, MESSAGENAME, BUSINESSOBJECTID, REQUESTID, PROCESSINSTANCEID, IMPLEMENTATIONCODE, ERRORREPORTINGDATETIME, EXTRAINFO1, EXTRAINFO2, EXTRAINFO3, EXTRAINFO4, CREATEDONDATETIME) values (#[flowVars['SeqID']], #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'InterfaceName\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'Sender\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'Target\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'VerbCode\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ErrorCode\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ErrorMsg\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'Severity\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'TransactionID\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'MessageID\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'MessageName\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'BusinessObjectID\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'RequestID\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ProcessInstanceID\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ImplementationCode\']/text()')],(SELECT CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP_TZ(REPLACE(#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ReportingDateTime\']/text()')], 'T', ''), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS.FF3TZH:TZM') AS DATE) FROM dual), #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ExtraInfo1\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ExtraInfo2\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ExtraInfo3\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ExtraInfo4\']/text()')],(SELECT CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP_TZ(REPLACE(#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'CreationDateTime\']/text()')], 'T', ''), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS.FF3') AS DATE) FROM dual) ) into error_data_tbl (SEQID, Stacktrace, Payload) values (#[flowVars['SeqID']], #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'StackTrace\']/text()')], #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'Payload\']/text()')]) select * from dual

SELECT INTERFACENAME, VERBCODE, ERRORCODE, ERRORDESCRIPTION, "ACTION", RESOLUTION, EMAILTO, EMAILSUBJECT, ERRORSEND_ENABLED, EMAILSENTDATETIME, EMAILDIGESTIONFLAG, EMAILDIGESTIONDURATION FROM ERROR_CONFIGURATION_TBL WHERE ((INTERFACENAME = #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'InterfaceName\']/text()')]) AND (ERRORCODE = #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ErrorCode\']/text()')]))

Insert all INTO Error_Repository_tbl (SEQID, INTERFACENAME, SENDER, TARGET, VERBCODE, ERRORCODE, ERRORMSG, SEVERITY, TRANSACTIONID, MESSAGEID, MESSAGENAME, BUSINESSOBJECTID, REQUESTID, PROCESSINSTANCEID, IMPLEMENTATIONCODE, ERRORREPORTINGDATETIME, EXTRAINFO1, EXTRAINFO2, EXTRAINFO3, EXTRAINFO4, CREATEDONDATETIME) values (seq_error_repo.nextval, #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'InterfaceName\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'Sender\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'Target\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'VerbCode\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ErrorCode\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ErrorMsg\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'Severity\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'TransactionID\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'MessageID\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'MessageName\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'BusinessObjectID\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'RequestID\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ProcessInstanceID\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ImplementationCode\']/text()')],(SELECT CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP_TZ(REPLACE(#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ReportingDateTime\']/text()')], 'T', ''), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS.FF3TZH:TZM') AS DATE) FROM dual), #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ExtraInfo1\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ExtraInfo2\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ExtraInfo3\']/text()')],#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ExtraInfo4\']/text()')],(SELECT CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP_TZ(REPLACE(#[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'CreationDateTime\']/text()')], 'T', ''), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS.FF3') AS DATE) FROM dual) ) into error_data_tbl (SEQID, Stacktrace, Payload) values (seq_error_repo.nextval, #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'StackTrace\']/text()')], #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'Payload\']/text()')]) select * from dual
select * from ERROR_CONFIGURATION_TBL where INTERFACENAME=#[flowVars['interfaceName']] AND ERRORCODE=#[flowVars['errorCode']]
select count(*) as count from ERROR_CONFIGURATION_TBL where INTERFACENAME=#[flowVars['interfaceName']] AND ERRORCODE=#[flowVars['errorCode']]
select count(*) as countError from ERROR_CONFIGURATION_TBL where INTERFACENAME=#[flowVars['interfaceName']] AND ERRORCODE=#[flowVars['errorCode']]
SELECT seq_error_repo.nextval as SeqID from dual

SELECT INTERFACENAME, VERBCODE, ERRORCODE, ERRORDESCRIPTION, "ACTION", RESOLUTION, EMAILTO, EMAILSUBJECT, ERRORSEND_ENABLED, EMAILSENTDATETIME, EMAILDIGESTIONFLAG, EMAILDIGESTIONDURATION FROM ERROR_CONFIGURATION_TBL WHERE ((INTERFACENAME = #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'InterfaceName\']/text()')]) AND (ERRORCODE = #[xpath3('//*[local-name() =\'ErrorCode\']/text()')]))

select count(*) as flag FROM error_configuration_tbl where sysdate > (select (EMAILSENTDATETIME+(EMAILDIGESTIONDURATION/1440)) FROM error_configuration_tbl where interfacename=#[flowVars['interfaceName']] and ERRORCODE=#[flowVars['errorCode']])
update error_repository_tbl set EMAILSENT='Y' where seqid = #[flowVars['SeqID']]
update error_repository_tbl set EMAILSENT='N' where seqid = #[flowVars['SeqID']]
update ERROR_CONFIGURATION_TBL SET EMAILSENTDATETIME=SYSDATE where INTERFACENAME=#[flowVars['interfaceName']] AND ERRORCODE=#[flowVars['errorCode']]
update error_repository_tbl set EMAILSENT='Y' where seqid in (select max(seqid) from error_repository_tbl)
update error_repository_tbl set EMAILSENT='N' where seqid in (select max(seqid) from error_repository_tbl)
